{"total":16,"pageSize":10,"pageCount":2,"data":[{"title":"广东工业大学2021广东省招生计划和排位","slug":"ranking","date":"2021-06-26T12:53:13.000Z","updated":"2021-06-26T13:02:46.146Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ranking.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"/images/posts/ranking/cover.png","content":"<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rhythmor/site/master/images/posts/ranking/ranking.png\" alt=\" 广东工业大学2021广东省招生计划和排位\"></p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"招生计划","path":"api/tags/招生计划.json"},{"name":"排位","path":"api/tags/排位.json"}]},{"title":"admission","slug":"admission","date":"2021-06-26T06:08:19.000Z","updated":"2021-06-26T06:08:19.363Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/admission.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"招生咨询QQ群","slug":"groups","date":"2021-06-26T05:31:04.000Z","updated":"2021-06-26T06:03:23.138Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/groups.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"粤东地区\"><a href=\"#粤东地区\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"粤东地区\"></a>粤东地区</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=KY4L2PLvQiXm8UjLSLpMu1eez8pbPXg7&authKey=Kybd6k03H7PllbFjVvuWf5Icf4lwQMt4VMBl8yP+hS71Ipf+BhHntltDZDRJhlE7&noverify=0\">潮州市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=_R-AdMlzKwSwRc-2a3mQjmsfsgkDlTL0&authKey=58nQWQpQIC08VLddjB20mULwQy1wgI9d1KEdnt6lQqyYUg+fwfh4XyQAl49OIOE5&noverify=0\">揭阳市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=4DCCvlSGPyxT-jQgCONQ_vMVOLgl5uRz&authKey=XxJ+DBxrOfyCdb5mEEE+nZqsvb+L6xmBRWXjly5WzHkEv65gRhV8dm2n/08/DmyR&noverify=0\">汕头市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=qvokQHEz13QXGslUPjPYAmad6ALvBPeK&authKey=XrTFLR9MgUc5UMOsEC+ij44HwARbHq7SC3OoupYeBTEuzJ39LAXqNjTi46iTGbZR&noverify=0\">汕尾市</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"珠三角地区\"><a href=\"#珠三角地区\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"珠三角地区\"></a>珠三角地区</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=RqFvUQMkFzj1zmg7vuzpGW__-bGJi-uM&authKey=y7ik7aUUPdXtfRyyBP5Pi0Fii1n7rvI9jW3RwNKdErzYQ/ZR7jJGbZFp8IynX11w&noverify=0\">东莞市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=sZNX8P5FYQY8i5bmCqe1NycNunAoqcpW&authKey=xtrpVb2IRUmltQqR8U1WNtiYB1Zi8jOfPj7rj2N5knG3/qfBDSGG0CY3+3sRT2iE&noverify=0\">佛山市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=yZJ8Lbv5JEIyEzdUqd31F9QBNCRuglbi&authKey=zqWs94Iu+IbFdH5uNz2ygRHPoCrvk+kfBAsk0K4K/KscdA7MjKgDOwv5sqyaOwvn&noverify=0\">广州市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=ceGwQwuDa9aqnWOhqzmcfahPLjRGPiha&authKey=82rY0RA/FNEAzNvAzvYGEJvGv9IMwUfjg7kOJZVNv926f3u00+DSHMnqzbFw74U3&noverify=0\">中山市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=6i5Gj19o0kCqq_UvmHTtGKdKdL8cCssT&authKey=t4xHqnojJvM1SSXOXWA59q8yc5GUUGfrv169DtlLShujgGkPpSvucJ08ANIisXj3&noverify=0\">江门市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=IYCzdWidiB49AA46Iuqz3MxYlvrCqR0V&authKey=xSqdcNpOukqkQULYMCmYLwGeYyrg93kGb0+QLnDXZZN4xdMGtfoY8JpSomoAil0X&noverify=0\">惠州市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=MCc6GsCggeF97P6I8K_mtUg6LvPtORPP&authKey=MClBR3arykzwhb4PwJUwO/Mqpskj4LQfjIwBxtQw+ocnTxviMc6kMDMtWH6qWO7S&noverify=0\">珠海市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=cEf9saTjeosv0oFS_14gRkSDjPC9q214&authKey=c0PR1Rn+NF6R2Kdgt4yWOiTtArWLNzNtXqX/eEoXbHjTG9lY6djNGIG4A7fQWBoT&noverify=0\">深圳市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=-kfFLnV7FYpuRiJhD8QY8nUF7u2AUDcH&authKey=Tc8JhwM1mDQp8gDoWeIBL2KdEtrkgSfje84tcZSZA137U79cUkzkMk4ueOGzJeIN&noverify=0\">肇庆市</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"粤北地区\"><a href=\"#粤北地区\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"粤北地区\"></a>粤北地区</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=N2yYPTxZFjpf8_HkPEJ0C3t_kXhatlNU&authKey=DxzKYA48TLb6VG4/YPZbimLvjeAqYPnSPAXMFxvX0GyhURsCTqd+pw4Cd8jeahVl&noverify=0\">河源市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=nTZYPEweW80gzi-tyBcNswDhFO2RYXoJ&authKey=8ZITIV28xV+XCNl9NFv1ndAMRpV1xUsVcTDp+ppIXdwMR/B7P5pbVWhjgaOd81te&noverify=0\">梅州市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=cNA4cWUKVIZ1XPcQsMoB2Qhwn1RLp8in&authKey=jju2eGFfZkKQP7HmoiFuvTYChB8yDkEfWBV34q7e5L4KdrpiKuIlLuiUj5FUAEGn&noverify=0\">云浮市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=hiYxEEmIPXUu_Pq3efbE1JN8yuLpKgy6&authKey=/aol9D0eaYdxYtbSlYNMn3aCIYaEn/RUCuXnZ6yk4+I4atrkvrdKbXfy3Xg5xFaF&noverify=0\">韶关市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=mPD5rLEdh_oCfAp0N-Ah34jiksZDFEqb&authKey=qt6yajrtJGrYTsMUXtvEXUgnXyccBiltuXR4T/b/G7p7boQdNtS5Kpc6zMEnwBPH&noverify=0\">清远市</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"粤西地区\"><a href=\"#粤西地区\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"粤西地区\"></a>粤西地区</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=e1Yu22bsOqJR1cWJs9kxoN5qYj_9J0W1&authKey=FL0SVKO7y6wJjlQA686W64mtuxihUS32S/hD7hRENcRz40KATp+C9Is8fL2Fejg1&noverify=0\">湛江市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=LsOPnCoZjxglK7ark8gHyGtQ44YuZrUw&authKey=S5M5tfa5elvKMoSpRXZXdSW1ctSn/8G+MpuU52tLyg1AHFo8iiKtrfmXcWejG4hC&noverify=0\">阳江市</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=5_pxFPHt-34CA6TaMYQlHy8cvHBrJA7p&authKey=9SaeOOGKybutAMIftiv2d8Ge/gHFVLMieViJHuyec2Ey/AAy6JA73ckjOOjJGxU+&noverify=0\">茂名市</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"广东省外、艺术类、揭阳校区、国际学院\"><a href=\"#广东省外、艺术类、揭阳校区、国际学院\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"广东省外、艺术类、揭阳校区、国际学院\"></a>广东省外、艺术类、揭阳校区、国际学院</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=k5Q69NoidrGT7gv2CVdWot7-fBVpoGUZ&authKey=xGWuKy9/1xEK0FeCXV7xEqiqNG8o2CT6Dhh17+3fGzjj8BHoFnOtET6mM2GK9ssA&noverify=0\">广东省外</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=GoSPc54xRC_Wjst7UYQ-mKAclsu-ErhO&authKey=Vm7HaI5tLeiMBLc6DKpfngtew+np91/FOPesOCvxttS5qpQwoXy7oFZAKgn5mstQ&noverify=0\">艺术类</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=uHu9gJpqRCrMFwxfwdkmn4l1JOyXhPYY&authKey=9dBmx14pjvbR7T3sMofe5MEhr0efALAwN5y67S5+14iWM5ZvdvBJgXnNWo1bQj01&noverify=0\">揭阳校区</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=MyzReVwx1XrAIMjjI7e-frQ5MrjrXkbQ&authKey=B9ZWgtI7/P50k5wfU2jkDxWzUy8Sew5JfEtSA5ySgvcxswOMKlrF7rEbVzg8Qst5&noverify=0\">国际学院</a></li>\n</ul>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"学费","slug":"fee","date":"2021-06-25T16:15:47.000Z","updated":"2021-06-26T05:30:41.751Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/fee.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"<p>学费与住宿费<br>（1）学费（不含书费）<br>①理工、外语类专业每生每年6850 元；文史、财经、管理<br>类专业每生每年6060 元；艺术类每生每年10000 元。<br>②戏剧与影视学类（中外合作办学）（动画）专业每生每年<br>28000 元；<br>③机械设计制造及其自动化（国际班）、电气工程及其自动<br>化（国际班）、土木工程（国际班）、计算机科学与技术（国际<br>班）、工商管理（国际班）学生因第1、2 学年在广东工业大学<br>学习期间，增加了双语教学、语言强化、专业培训等课程，除了<br>向广东工业大学缴纳相应专业的标准学费、住宿费和代收费外，<br>还应缴纳经广东省发展和改革委员会备案的双语教学、语言强化、<br>专业培训等费用两年共50000 元。<br>④港澳台联合招生、香港免试生学费标准与内地学生一致。<br>（2）住宿费<br>①大学城校区有空调设备的宿舍每生每年1700 元，没空调<br>设备的宿舍每生每年1500 元；<br>②龙洞校区有空调设备的宿舍每生每年1700 元，没空调设<br>备的宿舍每生每年1500 元；<br>③东风路校区每生每年750 -1400 元不等，由学校统一安排<br>住宿；<br>④番禺校区每生每年1700 元，<br>收费标准若有更改以广东省发展和改革委员会最新核定为准。</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"转专业","slug":"changemajor","date":"2021-06-25T16:12:20.000Z","updated":"2021-06-26T12:50:49.397Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/changemajor.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>广东工业大学本科生转专业实施办法 <a href=\"http://news.gdut.edu.cn/DepartmentUploadFiles/%E6%95%99%E5%8A%A1%E5%A4%84/files/1_%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E6%9C%AC%E7%A7%91%E7%94%9F%E8%BD%AC%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%88%E5%B9%BF%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%A7%E8%A7%84%E5%AD%97%E3%80%942015%E3%80%952%E5%8F%B7%E9%99%84%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%89.doc\">下载</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"转专业","path":"api/tags/转专业.json"}]},{"title":"绿色通道","slug":"greenway","date":"2021-06-25T15:44:15.000Z","updated":"2021-06-25T16:13:39.528Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/greenway.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"“绿色通道”\"><a href=\"#“绿色通道”\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"“绿色通道”\"></a>“绿色通道”</h1><p>指家庭经济特别困难的新生如暂时筹集不齐学费和住宿费，可在开学报到期间，通过学校开设的“绿色通道”先办理入学手续。</p>\n<p>新生报到时，我校各校区均设有“绿色通道”接待点，即对被录取入学、家庭经济困难的新生，学校一律先办理入学手续，然后再根据核实后的情况，通过国家助学贷款、勤工助学等方式予以资助来解决经济困难的问题。</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"绿色通道","path":"api/tags/绿色通道.json"}]},{"title":"勤工助学","slug":"employment","date":"2021-06-25T15:41:36.000Z","updated":"2021-06-25T15:42:38.622Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/employment.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"<p>学校每年为学生开设1000多个校内勤工助学固定岗和临时岗，协助学校各教学、管理、教辅部门开展“助教、助管、助研、学生辅导员、学风督导、生活督导、助学”等类型的工作。学生可自愿申请参加。校内勤工助学不仅是资助工作的重要组成部分，还是学校实践育人的重要平台。</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"勤工助学","path":"api/tags/勤工助学.json"}]},{"title":"助学贷款","slug":"loan","date":"2021-06-25T15:37:11.000Z","updated":"2021-06-25T15:39:50.973Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/loan.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"<p>党和政府设立国家助学贷款，用于帮助家庭经济困难学生解决学费和住宿费等问题。其中本科生每年申请金额不超过8000元，研究生不超过12000元，利率按照中国人民银行公布的法定贷款利率和国家有关利率政策执行。贷款学生在校学习期间（学制内）的国家助学贷款利息全部由财政补贴，毕业当年9月1日后的利息由贷款学生本人全额支付。贷款期限内可只还利息不还本金，贷款到期当年需偿还剩余本金和利息。学生可在入学前到户籍所在地的县级资助中心（或教育局）申请办理，办理后携《生源地信用贷款受理证明》（回执）入学报到。</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"奖助学金","slug":"scholarship","date":"2021-06-25T15:29:20.000Z","updated":"2021-06-25T15:38:25.072Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/scholarship.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/butterfly-extsrc@1/img/default.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"国家奖助学金\"><a href=\"#国家奖助学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"国家奖助学金\"></a>国家奖助学金</h1><h2 id=\"国家奖学金\"><a href=\"#国家奖学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"国家奖学金\"></a>国家奖学金</h2><ul>\n<li>本科生8000元/人·年</li>\n<li>硕士生20000元/人·年</li>\n<li>博士生30000元/人·年</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"国家励志奖学金\"><a href=\"#国家励志奖学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"国家励志奖学金\"></a>国家励志奖学金</h2><ul>\n<li>本科生5000元/人·年</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"国家助学金\"><a href=\"#国家助学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"国家助学金\"></a>国家助学金</h2><ul>\n<li>本科生（含预科生）2300-4000元/人·年</li>\n<li>硕士生6000元/人·年</li>\n<li>博士生13000元/人·年</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"学校奖助学金\"><a href=\"#学校奖助学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"学校奖助学金\"></a>学校奖助学金</h2><h3 id=\"本科生优秀学生奖学金\"><a href=\"#本科生优秀学生奖学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本科生优秀学生奖学金\"></a>本科生优秀学生奖学金</h3><ul>\n<li>一等奖2000元/人</li>\n<li>二等奖1000元/人</li>\n<li>三等奖600元/人</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"研究生学业奖学金\"><a href=\"#研究生学业奖学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"研究生学业奖学金\"></a>研究生学业奖学金</h3><ul>\n<li>硕士生2000-10000元/人·年</li>\n<li>博士生12000-18000元/人·年</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"单项奖学金\"><a href=\"#单项奖学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"单项奖学金\"></a>单项奖学金</h3><ul>\n<li>学习标兵奖学金</li>\n<li>优秀学生干部奖学金</li>\n<li>学生创新奖学金</li>\n<li>校园文艺菁英奖学金</li>\n<li>社会实践菁英奖学金</li>\n<li>学业进步奖学金。<br>奖金从100-1000元/人不等。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"学校助学金\"><a href=\"#学校助学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"学校助学金\"></a>学校助学金</h3><ul>\n<li>本科生1000-2000元/人/次</li>\n<li>博士生16000元/人·年</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"社会奖助学金\"><a href=\"#社会奖助学金\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"社会奖助学金\"></a>社会奖助学金</h2><p>　　目前校院两级已设立旭晟奖学金、真维斯助学金、仲明助学金、新力苏青助学金、“长江公益-精英助力计划”助学金等共计20多项社会、企业奖助学金。</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"奖学金","path":"api/tags/奖学金.json"},{"name":"助学金","path":"api/tags/助学金.json"}]},{"title":"自行车","slug":"bicycle","date":"2021-06-25T14:37:21.000Z","updated":"2021-06-26T15:28:17.770Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/bicycle.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"/images/posts/bicycle/cover.jpg","content":"<p>校园出行一般是走路，也可以买自行车代步。但是新车子很容易被偷。上午买了，中午被偷是很常见的现象。所以一定要买一把好的锁，最好不止一把锁。在锁单车时尽量找有栏杆的地方或者宿舍楼下，切忌放在空旷的室外。另外建议购买二手车，这样被偷的概率会减小。</p>\n<p>东区东九可以修车，也可以去南亭修，买的话南亭二手山地车大约150元，新的两百多起步，北亭的单车会便宜点。</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"交通出行","path":"api/categories/交通出行.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"自行车","path":"api/tags/自行车.json"},{"name":"共享单车","path":"api/tags/共享单车.json"}]}]}